description: Navigate to DEL style @ Shin Umeda by Daiwa Roynet. Head east along the main road, passing under a yellow pedestrian bridge and past a 7-Eleven on the left. Continue straight past the Daiwa Roynet Hotel building and turn left at the corner immediately after it (before the 'GYM FIELD' building). The destination entrance will be on the left side of this side street.
